John Sautkulis, Appellant, v. Frances Conklin et al., Respondents. William Matzok et al., Respondents, v. John Sautkulis, Appellant. (Action No. 1.) (Action No. 2)

(Consolidated Actions.)

Argued January 21, 1957; decided March 8, 1957. *920Nathan Dorfman and David Quient for appellant. Paul J. Leach for William Matzok and another, respondents.

Judgment affirmed, with costs to respondents Matzok; no opinion.

Concur: Conway, Ch. J., Desmond, Dye, Fuld, Froessel, Van Voorhis and Burke, JJ.
